<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">Dear All,</p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">I trust you have had a wonderful first week at Imperial! If you're new, I'm sure between the departments, halls and societies that you've been taken care of. If you are returning, I hope London has retained its charm﻿!</p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">TL;DR? Here's an update on last week and next week<br />
- We've had a great week running EESoc events last week!<br />
- Winner of Instagram #EESoc competition!<br />
- Meet the Team<br />
- Lockers on sale from Monday 14 October<br />
- Book Sale on Wednesday 16 October, 12-14<br />
- Updates from two of our sponsors, BP and Deutsche Bank</p>

<h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;display: block;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 22px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 300;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: left;color: #606060 !important"><a href="http://bit.ly/1a9ETgL" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline">#EESoc</a> Freshers' Week Photos</h3>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left"><a href="http://bit.ly/1bYcmy4" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline"><img src="https://eesoc.com/assets/email/uploads/email_1_5.jpg" width="550" style="width: 550px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;-ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;height: auto !important" /></a></p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">Congratulations to the Heaffey-Zhang family for this lovely photo spelling out EESoc. You've won EESoc t-shirts!</p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">Second place goes to <a href="http://bit.ly/1fYSjEQ" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline">Helen Root's video of Angry Birds Icebreaker projects</a>.</p>
<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">And taking third place home, <a href="http://bit.ly/1gpr7g2" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline">some Freshers' and their parents go to Scoop</a>!</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnDividerBlock" style="border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody class="mcnDividerBlockOuter"><tr><td class="mcnDividerBlockInner" style="padding: 10px 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                <table class="mcnDividerContent" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-top-width: 1px;border-top-style: solid;border-top-color: #CCC;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody><tr><td style="mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                            <span></span>
                        </td>
                    </tr></tbody></table></td>
        </tr></tbody></table><h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;display: block;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 22px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 300;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: left;color: #606060 !important">Meet the Team and see what we have planned</h3>
<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">Remember that video we showed Freshers' and parents on the first day? Yup. That very cheesy one. <a href="http://bit.ly/16wDIdD" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline">Watch it again, and laugh!</a></p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">See what we have planned in what will be an action packed Autumn term. Watch the <a href="http://bit.ly/19yPDdj" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline">launch video</a>:</p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left"><a href="http://bit.ly/1bGxPPk" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline"><img src="https://eesoc.com/assets/email/uploads/email_1_1.jpg" width="550" style="width: 550px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;-ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;height: auto !important" /></a></p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnDividerBlock" style="border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody class="mcnDividerBlockOuter"><tr><td class="mcnDividerBlockInner" style="padding: 10px 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                <table class="mcnDividerContent" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-top-width: 1px;border-top-style: solid;border-top-color: #CCC;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody><tr><td style="mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                            <span></span>
                        </td>
                    </tr></tbody></table></td>
        </tr></tbody></table><h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;display: block;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 22px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 300;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: left;color: #606060 !important">Locker Sale</h3>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">As you may know, we have three floors of lockers for you, our members. These can be rented out for £5 for the year. Interested? Lockers will go on sale online on Monday (14 October) at <strong>9:00 AM</strong>. We will send out an email about this once the lockers are ready to be sold.</p>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">Own a locker from last year? <strong>Please vacate your locker by Monday</strong>, as any locked locker will be opened and emptied after this date. Send us an email if you cannot empty your locker by then. Under certain circumstances, we will also let you keep your locker from last year; please <a href="mailto:eesoc@imperial.ac.uk" style="word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #6DC6DD;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline">let us know</a>.</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnDividerBlock" style="border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody class="mcnDividerBlockOuter"><tr><td class="mcnDividerBlockInner" style="padding: 10px 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                <table class="mcnDividerContent" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-top-width: 1px;border-top-style: solid;border-top-color: #CCC;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody><tr><td style="mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                            <span></span>
                        </td>
                    </tr></tbody></table></td>
        </tr></tbody></table><h3 style="margin: 0;padding: 0;display: block;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 22px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 300;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: left;color: #606060 !important">Book Sale</h3>

<p style="margin: 1em 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Trade Gothic W01 Light&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left">The book sale will be held on <strong>Wednesday 16 October</strong> from 12:00 until 14:00. More information will be sent about this shortly. This year we will have an online system so will easily be able to see what's available in advance.</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnDividerBlock" style="border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody class="mcnDividerBlockOuter"><tr><td class="mcnDividerBlockInner" style="padding: 10px 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                <table class="mcnDividerContent" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-top-width: 1px;border-top-style: solid;border-top-color: #CCC;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%"><tbody><tr><td style="mso-table-lspace: 0;mso-table-rspace: 0;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%">
                            <span></span>
                        </td>
                    </tr></tbody></table></td>
